{"id":17,"date":"2024-03-12T13:24:49","date_gmt":"2024-03-12T13:24:49","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/a-propos\/"},"modified":"2024-04-08T06:38:28","modified_gmt":"2024-04-08T06:38:28","slug":"bts-sio","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/bts-sio\/","title":{"rendered":"BTS SIO"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-background-background-color has-background is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-7 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--60);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image alignwide size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1088\" height=\"190\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_002327982.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-46\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_002327982.png 1088w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_002327982-300x52.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_002327982-1024x179.png 1024w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_002327982-768x134.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1088px) 100vw, 1088px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-5 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Le BTS SIO (Services Informatiques aux Organisations) est un dipl\u00f4me de l&rsquo;enseignement sup\u00e9rieur en France, principalement d\u00e9livr\u00e9 par les lyc\u00e9es et les \u00e9tablissements de formation technique. Ce dipl\u00f4me est ax\u00e9 sur les technologies de l&rsquo;information et de la communication (TIC) et vise \u00e0 former des professionnels capables de r\u00e9pondre aux besoins informatiques des organisations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-1 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-huge-font-size\" style=\"margin-bottom:1rem\">Le BTS SIO se d\u00e9cline en deux options principales :<\/h4>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:48px\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-palette-color-1-border-color has-tertiary-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-1 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003721736.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-50\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003721736.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003721736-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size:clamp(16.293px, 1.018rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.68), 25px);font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:capitalize\">SISR<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Option SISR (Solutions d&rsquo;Infrastructure, Syst\u00e8mes et R\u00e9seaux): Cette option se concentre sur la gestion des infrastructures informatiques, la configuration des syst\u00e8mes d&rsquo;exploitation, la gestion des r\u00e9seaux informatiques, la s\u00e9curit\u00e9 informatique, et la maintenance des \u00e9quipements.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-border-color has-vivid-purple-border-color has-tertiary-background-color has-background is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"border-width:5px;box-shadow:var(--wp--preset--shadow--sharp)\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full ext-aspect-landscape\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003711536.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-49\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003711536.png 300w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_003711536-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-container-core-group-is-layout-3 wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\" style=\"margin-top:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"font-size:clamp(16.293px, 1.018rem + ((1vw - 3.2px) * 0.68), 25px);font-style:normal;font-weight:700;text-transform:capitalize\">SLAM<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Option SLAM (Solutions Logicielles et Applications M\u00e9tiers): Cette option met l&rsquo;accent sur le d\u00e9veloppement de logiciels, la programmation, la conception d&rsquo;applications web et mobiles, la gestion de bases de donn\u00e9es, et l&rsquo;analyse des besoins m\u00e9tiers pour d\u00e9velopper des solutions informatiques adapt\u00e9es.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgb(6,147,227) 0%,rgb(255,255,255) 49%,rgb(155,81,224) 100%)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-1 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/sisr\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\">en savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-2 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/slam\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\">en savoir plus<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Le BTS SIO est une formation de niveau bac+2 et dure deux ans. Il offre une base solide dans les domaines de l&rsquo;informatique et des TIC, pr\u00e9parant les \u00e9tudiants \u00e0 des m\u00e9tiers comme administrateur syst\u00e8me, technicien r\u00e9seau, d\u00e9veloppeur web, d\u00e9veloppeur d&rsquo;applications, technicien de support informatique, etc.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Apr\u00e8s l&rsquo;obtention du BTS SIO, les \u00e9tudiants peuvent choisir de poursuivre leurs \u00e9tudes en obtenant une licence professionnelle, un Bachelor en informatique, ou m\u00eame de s&rsquo;ins\u00e9rer directement dans le monde du travail. Ce dipl\u00f4me est reconnu dans de nombreuses entreprises qui recherchent des professionnels comp\u00e9tents en informatique pour r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 leurs besoins en mati\u00e8re de gestion de l&rsquo;information et de la technologie.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Le BTS SIO (Services Informatiques aux Organisations) est un dipl\u00f4me de l&rsquo;enseignement sup\u00e9rieur en France, principalement d\u00e9livr\u00e9 par les lyc\u00e9es et les \u00e9tablissements de formation technique. Ce dipl\u00f4me est ax\u00e9 sur les technologies de l&rsquo;information et de la communication (TIC) et vise \u00e0 former des professionnels capables de r\u00e9pondre aux besoins informatiques des organisations. Le [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"no-title","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-17","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"blocksy_meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/17","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17"}],"version-history":[{"count":17,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/17\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":850,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/17\/revisions\/850"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}